.DT
slash
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
slash

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
slash - perform a slashing attack in combat
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
slash <target> [with] <weapon>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to perform a slashing attack. Note that you must be in combat to perform this, you must be using a sharp weapon, and you must be concentrating on your target (if you are fighting more than one enemy).
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> slash rat with sword
.EI
